V<div class="inset-shadow"><img src="images/Survival_Training.png"></div>\u000aThe Global Education Office welcomes you to ''Study Abroad Survival Training''. The training modules within introduce you to a wealth of information, information that you will need to know to have a successful and safe experience abroad. Please read everything carefully.\u000a\u000aYou can take the Quick Tour now for a very brief introduction to the Training interface. It will very quickly show you what all of the elements on this page are and what they do. <<button "Take the Tour">><<script>>ga('send', 'event', 'help', 'tour', 'launched tour from intro page'); activateHelp();<</script>><</button>>\u000a\u000aFrom time to time, you will see a red box like the one below that provides more detailed information on a topic or topics. Just click on the red links to check them out.\u000a\u000a<<sidebar-box "In-Depth Information">>\u000a   [[Click here for a sample, just to see how it works!|Sample]]\u000a<</sidebar-box>>\u005c\u000a\u000aWhen you're ready to move on, hit the big blue Continue button at the bottom of the page!\u000a\u000a!!!!!Browser support\u000aThis presentation works best with recent versions of the major browsers on desktops, tablets, and smartphones. If you are having trouble with the presentation, try upgrading your web browser. Or you may [[download the presentation in PDF format|#]] instead.\u000a\u000a<<display "Browsers">>\u005c\u000a\u000a<<segue "What you will get out of study abroad">>\u005c\u000a/% !!!!Choose mode to continue\u000aThis presentation can be viewed in Automatic Mode, with a narrator speaking the text, or in Manual Mode. You can turn Automatic Mode on or off at any time using the button in the upper right.\u000a\u000aYou can always hit the <span class='continue-button' style="clear:both;"><<click "Continue" $first>><<set options.autoplay to true>><<updateAutoplay>><<saveoptions>><</click>><span class="anim-wrapper"><span class='onwar